E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-hi%E1%BB%87u-th%C6%B0-t%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n/poem-dlHnmd0KjGsb0OLTGFEOjQ">Tống Lưu hiệu thư tòng quân - 送劉校書從軍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Qu%C3%BDnh/author-UC91PIpcFalgwS4PbK2Lpg">Dương Quýnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%E1%BB%91ng-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-San-Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-%C4%90%E1%BB%99-chi-h%E1%BA%ADu-b%E1%BB%95/poem-k7ykTHuxxMHtol7ZSY5EdA">Tống tiến sĩ Nguyễn Văn San, Ngô Văn Độ chi hậu bổ - 送進士阮文珊吳文度之候補</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Quan-%C3%82m-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-f76aMK64Up98A9l81s92VQ">Vọng Quan Âm miếu - 望觀音廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A4u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-L-yQw2T8IwQqeO9EhEtm_w">Vô đề (II) - 無題 (II)</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A4u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/author-ersmrUf9dYOiBelsjNNnnw">Vương Ấu Ngọc</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
